reviewText: One of the most fun exercise videos I have enjoyed.
Fantastic!!! Really gets me up to have fun and exercise. I first saw this sweet couple on Shark Tank. Wonderful for me . Trying some of these with my students.
The workout is okay. What I really disliked was the singing: it distracts from the workout and I must say her voice is not that pretty...
This seems pretty simple until you finish the video then you are sweating.  It really helped build up steps toward my 10K a day step plan.
I am very happy with this cd.
